<div class="row mb-4">
    <div class="col">
        <h1 class="fw-bold h3 mb-1">Upload Item CSV</h1>
        <p class="text-secondary">Impor data item secara massal menggunakan file CSV.</p>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="row">
    <div class="col-lg-6">
        <div class="card p-4">
            <form action="/items/upload" method="POST" enctype="multipart/form-data">
                <div class="mb-4">
                    <label for="csvFile" class="form-label fw-bold">Pilih File CSV</label>
                    <input class="form-control" type="file" id="csvFile" name="csvFile" accept=".csv" required>
                    <div class="form-text mt-2 small">Gunakan file CSV yang sesuai dengan template sistem.</div>
                </div>

                <div class="mb-4">
                    <label class="form-label fw-bold">Pilihan Delimiter</label>
                    <div class="d-flex flex-wrap gap-3 mt-1">
                        <div class="form-check">
                            <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="delimiter" id="comma" value="," checked>
                            <label class="form-check-label" for="comma">Koma (,)</label>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-check">
                            <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="delimiter" id="semicolon" value=";">
                            <label class="form-check-label" for="semicolon">Titik Koma (;)</label>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-check">
                            <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="delimiter" id="tab" value="tab">
                            <label class="form-check-label" for="tab">Tab</label>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-check">
                            <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="delimiter" id="pipe" value="pipe">
                            <label class="form-check-label" for="pipe">Pipe (|)</label>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="p-4 bg-light rounded border-start border-4 border-info mb-4">
                    <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-2">
                        <h6 class="fw-bold small mb-0 text-info">Struktur Kolom CSV yang Diperlukan:</h6>
                        <a href="/items/template" class="btn btn-sm btn-info text-white">Download Template</a>
                    </div>
                    <code
                        class="small text-secondary">brandCode, barcode, itemId, article, material, color, size, name, description, category, price, sellPrice, discount, isSpecialPrice, stockQty, printQty, pricingId</code>
                </div>

                <div class="mt-4">
                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary w-100 py-2">Mulai Proses Impor</button>
                    <a href="/items" class="btn btn-link w-100 text-secondary mt-2">Batal</a>
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-lg-6">
        <div class="card p-4 border-0 shadow-sm">
            <h6 class="fw-bold mb-3">Petunjuk Upload</h6>
            <ul class="small text-secondary ps-3">
                <li class="mb-2">Pastikan header CSV sesuai dengan nama field di atas (case sensitive).</li>
                <li class="mb-2">Jika `itemId` sudah ada di sistem, maka data item tersebut akan diperbarui
                    (**Upsert**).</li>
                <li class="mb-2">Field `itemId`, `brandCode`, dan `name` bersifat wajib/required.</li>
                <li>Gunakan encoding UTF-8 untuk menghindari karakter yang rusak.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>